OL,3,C'Cold-hearted' thieves steal statue
OL,4,Cfrom children's hospice
OL,6,FStaff at a children's hospice in West
OL,7,FSussex say they've been left in shock
OL,8,Fafter 'cold-hearted' thieves stole a
OL,9,Fstatue from their grounds.
OL,11,FThose working at Chestnut Tree House
OL,12,FHospice near Arundel have described
OL,13,Fthe incident as 'disrespectful' as
OL,14,Fit's happened just days before
OL,15,FChristmas.
OL,17,FThe statue of a boy playing on the
OL,18,Fground is part of a trio of sculptures
OL,19,Fshowing children playing and is
OL,20,Fpositioned outside near the hospice
OL,21,Fentrance.
