OL,3,C'Cold-hearted' thieves steal statue
OL,4,Cfrom children's hospice
OL,6,FThe set also features a little girl
OL,7,Fgazing at her hands and an older girl
OL,8,Fdancing.
OL,10,FThe statues, which were funded by a
OL,11,Fsupporter at a cost of over #5,000,
OL,12,Fwere installed in 2004, and have since
OL,13,Fbecome an iconic and much-loved
OL,14,Ffeature of the hospice grounds.
OL,16,FThe statue of the little boy sat
OL,17,Fplaying with a mouse was stolen from
OL,18,Fthe hospice grounds on Tuesday. (16
OL,19,FDecember)
