OL,3,C'Cold-hearted' thieves steal statue
OL,4,Cfrom children's hospice
OL,6,FSculptor Vanessa Marston created the
OL,7,Fstatues using bronze resin, and the
OL,8,Fhospice says the boy with the mouse
OL,9,Faims to capture the gentleness,
OL,10,Fintrigue and kind-nature of children,
OL,11,Fand reflects those who are being cared
OL,12,Ffor at the hospice.
OL,14,FKevin Blackett, Head of Operational
OL,15,FDelivery at Chestnut Tree House/
OL,16,FSouthern Hospice Group said: "This is
OL,17,Fsuch a cold-hearted and horrible thing
OL,18,Fto happen, it feels even worse
OL,19,Fhappening just before Christmas.
