OL,6,F"This is a special time of year for
OL,7,Four families, and this is so
OL,8,Fdisrespectful.
OL,10,F"The statues are distinctive, they
OL,11,Foffer families and children a
OL,12,Freassuring signal that they have
OL,13,Farrived at a place of care, sanctuary
OL,14,Fand play."
OL,16,FThe hospice are appealing to people to
OL,17,Fcheck online selling sites, social
OL,18,Fmedia marketplaces, or even at car
OL,19,Fboot sales for the stolen statue.
OL,21,FSussex Police are investigating.
